  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>You may choose for your poison to inflict a penalty of -2 to one ability score of the target (except Constitution) instead of making the target fatigued. The penalties from multiple applications of Degenerating Poison stack. For every 5 Craft (alchemy) ranks you possess, you may increase the penalty of this poison by -2. You may apply all of this penalty to a single ability score, or divide it in units of -2 between multiple ability scores. You choose which ability scores receive penalties, and how the penalty is divided, when creating this poison.</p>\n",
